title: Rakning C-19
description: Official app from the Icelandic Government to help mitigate the Covid-19 pandemic in Iceland The app collects the GPS location of the phone and stores locally on the device. If the phone owner is diagnosed with the Covid-19 disease he is asked by the Directorate of Health to share the location data for contact tracing in order to identify individuals that might need to go into quarantine.
